    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Splitter Sliding Clutch and Yoke</title>
        <para>Place splitter shift yoke into splitter sliding clutch slot. Install assembly onto auxiliary section
            engaging the sliding clutch teeth into the auxiliary drive gear clutching teeth and splitter yoke onto yoke
            bar (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f13027i2">Figure 182</hotlnk>). Align lockscrew, tighten to recommended torque and lockwire.
        </para>
        <figure id="f13027i2" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g13027i2" filename="../figg13/G13027i2.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 182. Install Assembly onto Auxiliary Section</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcsubproc>
